,"two_hundred_day_avg":83.89515,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":220.5,"all_time_low":36.45,"long_business_summary":"Tanvi Foods (India) Limited provides processed agricultural products, frozen snacks, and traditional regional frozen foods in India. The company offers frozen agri products, such as sweet corn, green pea, mixed vegetable, jackfruit, ivy gourd, carrot, drumstick, okra, beetroot, and green chilli; frozen snack products, including samosas, corn spring roll, paneer roll, shanghai roll, and chocolate roll, as well as veg bites, veg fingers, veg lollipop, and kebab; frozen dal and curries; and frozen vegetable chutneys. It also provides cold storage, warehousing, and refrigerated storekeeping; and cargo services. The company offers its products under the Frozen King's and Corn Club brand names. Tanvi Foods (India) Limited was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Hyderabad, India."}}